Lotus Technology generates revenues primarily through sales of goods and services. Sales of goods. Lotus Technology generates revenues by providing the following products: • BEV lifestyle models developed by Lotus Technology;  
• Lotus-brand sports cars developed by Lotus UK;  
• auto parts; and  
• peripheral products. Services.    Lotus Technology generates revenues mainly by providing automotive design and development services to OEM customers and after-sales service. The following table sets forth a breakdown of revenues by type both in absolute amount and as a percentage of Lotus Technology's revenues for the years indicated.

